body:
# PsynthJS
PsynthJS is a Javascript library for programmatically generating graphs in [Psymphonic Psynth](psymphonic.com).  It requires jQuery.

```
<script src="PATH TO JQUERY"></script>
<script src="js/psynth.js"></script>
```

### Authors and Contributors
This project is supported by [Psymphonic](psymphonic.com).

### Documentation
Check out the docs.
